<plot>This docudrama is the story of the great "Isicathamiya" South African singing group, Ladysmith Black Mambazo. This musical documentary, filmed in 1988, shows the immediate popularity they received from the audiences of the world and the winning of the now-famous Grammy Award for their first US album, "Shaka Zulu".</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?318021</url></doc>
